-- Packers to Sign Former Colts Center Jeff Saturday, ESPN Reports
-- B y   J a y   B e b e r m a n
-- 2012-03-23T16:54:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-23/packers-to-sign-former-colts-center-jeff-saturday-espn-reports.html
The  Green Bay Packers  agreed to
terms with former Indianapolis Colts center Jeff Saturday, ESPN
reported, citing unidentified people in the  National Football
League .  Saturday, 36, had played with the Colts and  Peyton Manning 
since 1999. Manning signed with Denver on March 20.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
